WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.275
Welcome to RestoreAssist.

00:03.275 --> 00:09.170
This is your complete account creation guide.

00:09.170 --> 00:16.245
Enter your email address and create a secure password.

00:16.245 --> 00:24.245
Add your business name and ABN — we verify it automatically against the Australian Business Register.

00:24.245 --> 00:30.009
Confirm your details and tap Create Account.

00:30.009 --> 00:38.009
The Setup Wizard guides you through five steps — business profile, AI hydration, integrations, health check, and activation.

00:38.009 --> 00:43.249
Tap Activate and your workspace is live.

00:43.249 --> 00:46.524
Welcome to RestoreAssist.